Pharmacology for Nursing Care
Author: Richard A. Lehne PhD

This money-saving package is a must-have for students! It includes Pharmacology for Nursing Care, 7th edition and an electronic version of the textbook that allows students to search, highlight information, take notes, share notes and more. This package makes it simple for students to make the most of their study time and get more use out of their textbooks!
